text:
PART I.  GENERAL PROVISIONS AND DEFINITIONS
 
Note
 
  Chapter repealed January 1, 2019.  L 2017, c 181, §§2, 47.
  This part, referenced as repealed in the main volume, was reenacted by L 2007, c 244, pt of §2.  Source notes for each section in this part begin with L 2007, c 244.
 
         This chapter shall be known as the Condominium Property Act. [L 2007, c 244, pt of §2]
